name: Confectioner
body:
### Welcome to Cofectioner project
Confectioner_Web is a social of confectioner. They can share information baker, recipe, product.
### Designer Templates
I used bootstrap 3.0 to code this project. Website is work well in desktop all tablet and mobile devices
### Support or Contact
You can visit https://github.com/hieudt7/confectioner to see more about my project.
